<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_07_IH_0002</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_07.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_07_ih_0002 paging">
			<section class="title type2 score">
				<h2 data-head="2_deep_green" lang="y">
					스티커 10개를 민하와 규민이가 1 : 4로 나누어 가지려고 합니다. 두 사람이 나누어 가지는 스티커는 각각
					몇 개인지 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
				</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents paging_layout">
				<article class="page page_1">
					<h3 lang="y">두 사람이 나누어 가지는 스티커의 수는 각각 전체의 몇 분의 몇인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
					<div class="question_box justify_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0002_01_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<p class="name" lang="y">민하</p>
								<div class="input_area">
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
											+
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
									</div>
									=
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="5" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0002_02_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<p class="name" lang="y">규민</p>
								<div class="input_area">
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
											+
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
									</div>
									=
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap">
												<math-field data-answer-single="5" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p>
										• 민하가 나누어 가지는 스티커의 수는 전체의
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>1</span>
										  <span>1+4</span>
										</span>
										= 
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>1</span>
										  <span>5</span>
										</span>이며,
										규민이가 나누어 가지는 스티커의 수는 전체의
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>4</span>
										  <span>1+4</span>
										</span>
										= 
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>4</span>
										  <span>5</span>
										</span>입니다.
									  </p>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="page page_2">
					<h3 lang="y">두 사람이 나누어 가지는 스티커는 각각 몇 개인지 구해 보세요.</h3>

					<div class="question_box justify_center">
						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0002_01_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<p class="name" lang="y">민하</p>
								<div class="input_area">
									10×
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span> 5 </span>
									</div>
									=
									<span class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
									</span>
									<span lang="y">(개)</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="img_area">
							<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_07_IH/0002_02_bg.png" alt="" />
							<div class="text_area">
								<p class="name" lang="y">규민</p>
								<div class="input_area">
									10×
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>
											<span class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="up">
												<math-field data-answer-single="4" class="w_80"></math-field>
											</span>
										</span>
										<span> 5 </span>
									</div>
									=
									<span class="input_wrap">
										<math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field>
									</span>
									<span lang="y">(개)</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- 해설 -->
					<div class="solve_area">
						<div class="inner_solve">
							<div class="flex">
								<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
								<div class="conts_solve">
									<p>
										• 스티커 10개를 1 : 4로 나눕니다.
									  </p>
									
									  <p>
										민하: 10 × 
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>1</span>
										  <span>5</span>
										</span>
										= 2(개)
									  </p>
									
									  <p>
										규민: 10 × 
										<span class="fraction_box align-middle">
										  <span>4</span>
										  <span>5</span>
										</span>
										= 8(개)
									  </p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="btn_area">
						<button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
						<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
						<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
					</div>
				</article>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
